description: Svenska Cellulosa AB engages in the business of forest products. The company is headquartered in Sundsvall, Vasternorrland and currently employs 3,829 full-time employees.  The firm owns forests that are located in northern Sweden. Svenska Cellulosa SCA is engaged in managing the forest and providing supplies from the paper industry. The firm offers paper for packaging and print, pulp, wood products, renewable energy, services for forest owners and efficient transport solutions.
name: Svenska Cellulosa SCA AB
